module advshift(
    input clk,
    input load,
    input ena,
    input [1:0] amount,
    input [63:0] data,
    output reg [63:0] q
);

always @(posedge clk) begin
    if (load) begin
        q <= data;
    end else if (ena) begin
        case (amount)
            2'b00: q <= {q[62:0], 1'b0}; // Shift left by 1 bit
            2'b01: q <= {q[55:0], 7'b0}; // Shift left by 8 bits
            2'b10: q <= {1'b0, q[63:1]}; // Shift right by 1 bit
            2'b11: q <= {8'b0, q[63:9]}; // Shift right by 8 bits
            default: q <= q; // No change if amount is not recognized
        endcase
    end
end

endmodule
